News.Title: Ken Enterprises: Weak Market Debut with 9.5% Discount on NSE SME
News.Summary: Ken Enterprises shares listed at ₹85 on NSE SME, 9.57% below the IPO price of ₹94. The ₹83.65 crore IPO was oversubscribed 4.36 times. Funds raised will be used for acquisitions, machinery purchase, and working capital requirements.
